description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience at this move-in ready 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath single-family home offering just under 1,000 sq. ft. of updated living space. With two parking spaces, thoughtful updates throughout, and a functional layout, this home is ideal for today’s lifestyle. Located steps from the Red Line and the transformative On the Dot development, the property sits in the heart of a rapidly growing neighborhood poised for long-term appreciation. For investors, it’s currently rented at $3,300/month TAW, providing immediate income in one of Boston’s most dynamic markets. For owner occupants, it’s a turnkey opportunity to enjoy private living with every city convenience right outside your door.
